{"tid":2094320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[若果o係美國]美3警模仿黑人被鎖頸致死動作拍照遭革職或辭職　一警見相回應「哈哈」同遭被炒","createTime":"2020-07-04T14:00:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T15:21:41.000Z","uid":51271,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b623acd639d20e1c6790d76b94536bca7a3a2270","tid":2094320,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:00:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20200704/s00005/1593869850366/%e7%be%8e3%e8%ad%a6%e6%a8%a1%e4%bb%bf%e9%bb%91%e4%ba%ba%e8%a2%ab%e9%8e%96%e9%a0%b8%e8%87%b4%e6%ad%bb%e5%8b%95%e4%bd%9c%e6%8b%8d%e7%85%a7%e9%81%ad%e9%9d%a9%e8%81%b7%e6%88%96%e8%be%ad%e8%81%b7-%e4%b8%80%e8%ad%a6%e8%a6%8b%e7%9b%b8%e5%9b%9e%e6%87%89%e3%80%8c%e5%93%88%e5%93%88%e3%80%8d%e5%90%8c%e9%81%ad%e8%a2%ab%e7%82%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200704%2Fs00005%2F1593869850366%2F%25e7%25be%258e3%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e6%25a8%25a1%25e4%25bb%25bf%25e9%25bb%2591%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e9%258e%2596%25e9%25a0%25b8%25e8%2587%25b4%25e6%25ad%25bb%25e5%258b%2595%25e4%25bd%259c%25e6%258b%258d%25e7%2585%25a7%25e9%2581%25ad%25e9%259d%25a9%25e8%2581%25b7%25e6%2588%2596%25e8%25be%25ad%25e8%2581%25b7-%25e4%25b8%2580%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e8%25a6%258b%25e7%259b%25b8%25e5%259b%259e%25e6%2587%2589%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%2593%2588%25e5%2593%2588%25e3%2580%258d%25e5%2590%258c%25e9%2581%25ad%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e7%2582%2592&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmqnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=428a03a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200704%2Fs00005%2F1593869850366%2F%25e7%25be%258e3%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e6%25a8%25a1%25e4%25bb%25bf%25e9%25bb%2591%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e9%258e%2596%25e9%25a0%25b8%25e8%2587%25b4%25e6%25ad%25bb%25e5%258b%2595%25e4%25bd%259c%25e6%258b%258d%25e7%2585%25a7%25e9%2581%25ad%25e9%259d%25a9%25e8%2581%25b7%25e6%2588%2596%25e8%25be%25ad%25e8%2581%25b7-%25e4%25b8%2580%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e8%25a6%258b%25e7%259b%25b8%25e5%259b%259e%25e6%2587%2589%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%2593%2588%25e5%2593%2588%25e3%2580%258d%25e5%2590%258c%25e9%2581%25ad%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e7%2582%2592&h=10d4e897\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20200704/s00005/1593869850366/%e7%be%8e3%e8%ad%a6%e6%a8%a1%e4%bb%bf%e9%bb%91%e4%ba%ba%e8%a2%ab%e9%8e%96%e9%a0%b8%e8%87%b4%e6%ad%bb%e5%8b%95%e4%bd%9c%e6%8b%8d%e7%85%a7%e9%81%ad%e9%9d%a9%e8%81%b7%e6%88%96%e8%be%ad%e8%81%b7-%e4%b8%80%e8%ad%a6%e8%a6%8b%e7%9b%b8%e5%9b%9e%e6%87%89%e3%80%8c%e5%93%88%e5%93%88%e3%80%8d%e5%90%8c%e9%81%ad%e8%a2%ab%e7%82%92</a><br />\n<br />\n美國科羅拉多州3名警員，因模仿去年8月一名黑人被警頸鎖的動作拍照。警方周五（3日）表示，其中兩名警員被革職、一人周二（6月30日）辭職；另一見到照片後以「哈哈」回應的警員同遭革職。<br />\n<br />\n去年8月，一名23歲黑人在科羅拉多奧荷拉（Aurora）被指「形迹可疑」，遭警員鎖頸制服，救護員到場後對事主注射麻醉用氯胺酮，他其後心臟停頓，數日後拔除維生儀器死亡，科羅拉多警方下令對其死因進行特別調查。<br />\n<br />\n3名警員在去年10月於事發地點附近，模仿事主被頸鎖動作拍照；另一警員見到照片後以「哈哈」回應。警方批評，涉事警員行為「令人作嘔」、「應受指摘」（reprehensible）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港黑狗仲個個身光頸靚</span>"},{"pid":"5fca828c2bd39a9df0555c99d734cf0f73e14fcf","tid":2094320,"uid":83582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:18:57.000Z","msg":"藍絲睇唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7057c644498e3d5928fbb074cdb034179f0f9074","tid":2094320,"uid":283700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:22:26.000Z","msg":"佢caption係講呢件事 就咁睇相真係唔覺 仲好似黑人黎"},{"pid":"01114741719a8254a2d8d2759b3774bde5c8c7d5","tid":2094320,"uid":136661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:25:06.000Z","msg":"如果係美國嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db8648124360b4c7568424786290bb42ce09f8a","tid":2094320,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:45:28.000Z","msg":"美國黑鬼matter<br />\n港豬dont matter"},{"pid"